     fhir:Narrative.div "<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><p class=\"res-header-id\"><b>Generated Narrative: ValueSet IMMZD18SRotavirusVS</b></p><a name=\"IMMZD18SRotavirusVS\"> </a><a name=\"hcIMMZD18SRotavirusVS\"> </a><p>This value set expansion contains 5 concepts.</p><table class=\"codes\"><tr><td><b>System</b></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Display</b></td><td><b>Definition</b></td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"IMMZD18SRotavirusVS-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK-Child's|20birth-0\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZDAK.html#IMMZDAK-Child.39sbirth-0\">Child's birth-0</a></td><td>Child's birth</td><td><div/></td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"IMMZD18SRotavirusVS-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK-First|20rotavirus|20dose|20from|20the|20primary|20series|20was|20administered-118\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZDAK.html#IMMZDAK-Firstrotavirusdosefromtheprimaryserieswasadministered-118\">First rotavirus dose from the primary series was administered-118</a></td><td>First rotavirus dose from the primary series was administered</td><td><div><p>Count of vaccines administered (where \"Vaccine type\" = \"Rotavirus vaccines\" and \"Type of dose\" = \"Primary series\") = 1</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"IMMZD18SRotavirusVS-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK-Second|20rotavirus|20dose|20from|20the|20primary|20series|20was|20administered-118\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZDAK.html#IMMZDAK-Secondrotavirusdosefromtheprimaryserieswasadministered-118\">Second rotavirus dose from the primary series was administered-118</a></td><td>Second rotavirus dose from the primary series was administered</td><td><div><p>Count of vaccines administered (where \"Vaccine type\" = \"Rotavirus vaccines\" and \"Type of dose\" = \"Primary series\") = 2</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"IMMZD18SRotavirusVS-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK-For|20a|20series|20containing|20more|20than|20two|20doses,|20two|20rotavirus|20primary|20series|20doses|20of|20mixed|20series|20or|20a|20series|20with|20unknown|20vaccine|20products|20were|20administered-324\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZDAK.html#IMMZDAK-Foraseriescontainingmorethantwodoses.44tworotavirusprimaryseriesdosesofmixedseriesoraserieswithunknownvaccineproductswereadministered-324\">For a series containing more than two doses, two rotavirus primary series doses of mixed series or a series with unknown vaccine products were administered-324</a></td><td>For a series containing more than two doses, two rotavirus primary series doses of mixed series or a series with unknown vaccine products were administered</td><td><div><p>Count of vaccines administered (where \"Vaccine type\" = \"Rotavirus vaccines\"and \"Type of dose\" = \"Primary series\" ) = 2\nAND \"Vaccine brand\" (where \"Vaccine type\" = \"Rotavirus vaccines\" AND \"Dose number\" = 1) ≠ \"Vaccine brand\" (where \"Vaccine type\" = \"Rotavirus vaccines\" AND \"Dose number\" = 2) OR \"Total doses in series\" &gt; 2</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"IMMZD18SRotavirusVS-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK-Third|20rotavirus|20dose|20from|20the|20primary|20series|20was|20administered-118\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZDAK.html#IMMZDAK-Thirdrotavirusdosefromtheprimaryserieswasadministered-118\">Third rotavirus dose from the primary series was administered-118</a></td><td>Third rotavirus dose from the primary series was administered</td><td><div><p>Count of vaccines administered (where \"Vaccine type\" = \"Rotavirus vaccines\" and \"Type of dose\" = \"Primary series\") = 3</p>\n</div></td></tr></table></div>"
